    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ceratomontia capensis Roewer, 1915, lectotype J (SMF 9801182-RI/1182-53), habitus: dorsal (A), lateral (B), ventral (C) and pedipalp (D). Scale bars (A─C) 2 mm, (D) 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10012708>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ceratomontia capensis Roewer 1915, lectotype J (SMF 9801182-RI/1182-53) genitalia: ventral view (A); lateral view (B); dorsal view (C). Abbreviations: ce, capsula externa; ci, capsula interna; vp, ventral plate. Scale bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10012708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

